notes: Big Canoe Project is a not-for-profit social enterprise getting people active on the waters of Southern Georgian Bay in our 29' canoe.  With the help of the Canadian Voyageur Brigades, the Ontario Recreational Canoeing and Kayaking Association, the Georgian Bay Biosphere, the Lake Huron Center for Coastal Conservation and Water Rangers we immerse people in the experience, teachings and best stewardship practices of the ecosystem we're lucky enough to call home.  While out on the water in Owen Sound, Meaford, Collingwood and Lake Eugenia, participants get involved with the collection of water quality data using kits supplied by Water Rangers.

notes_translated.en: Big Canoe Project is a not-for-profit social enterprise getting people active on the waters of Southern Georgian Bay in our 29' canoe.  With the help of the Canadian Voyageur Brigades, the Ontario Recreational Canoeing and Kayaking Association, the Georgian Bay Biosphere, the Lake Huron Center for Coastal Conservation and Water Rangers we immerse people in the experience, teachings and best stewardship practices of the ecosystem we're lucky enough to call home.  While out on the water in Owen Sound, Meaford, Collingwood and Lake Eugenia, participants get involved with the collection of water quality data using kits supplied by Water Rangers.
notes_translated.fr: Big Canoe Project est une entreprise sociale à but non lucratif qui permet aux gens de faire de l'activité sur les eaux du sud de la baie Georgienne à bord de notre canot de 29 pieds. Avec l'aide des Brigades des voyageurs canadiens, de l'Association ontarienne de canoë-kayak de loisir, de la biosphère de la baie Georgienne, du Lake Huron Center for Coastal Conservation et des Water Rangers, nous immergeons les gens dans l'expérience, les enseignements et les meilleures pratiques de gestion de l'écosystème dans lequel nous avons la chance de vivre. Sur l'eau à Owen Sound, Meaford, Collingwood et Lake Eugenia, les participants participent à la collecte de données sur la qualité de l'eau à l'aide de kits fournis par Water Rangers.
